The Algebraist (2004). London: Orbit. ISBN 1-84149-155-1
Transition (2009). London: Little, Brown Book Group. ISBN 978-0-316-73107-2. (Published in the United States as Iain M. Banks.)
The State of the Art (1991). London: Orbit. ISBN 0-356-19669-0 Includes three short works set in the Culture universe. It also includes works of fiction more characteristic of Banks's writing published as Iain Banks. A radio version of the title story was transmitted by Radio 4 in 2009.[79]
