The Science Fiction Foundation have published an analysis of Ken MacLeod's work titled The True Knowledge Of Ken MacLeod (2003; ISBN 0-903007-02-9), edited by Andrew M. Butler and Farah Mendlesohn. As well as critical essays and material on MacLeod, it includes MacLeod's introduction to the German edition of Banks' Consider Phlebas and essays comparing the works of the two authors.
